on, Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结：**\n\n1. **故障类型**：这是一次明确的**故障注入测试**，使用了Byteman工具对adservice服务进行stress压力测试\n2. **影响范围**：所有3个adservice实例（adservice-0, adservice-1, adservice-2）都受到影响\n3. **关键证据**：\n   - 日志中大量出现`AdService--stress-1749913849`规则执行记录\n   - 多个stress线程同时创建和运行（17499138490-17499138496）\n   - Byteman代理加载失败和重复加载异常\n4. **持续时间**：15分钟的压力测试期间，系统处于预期的异常状态\n\n这看起来是一次有计划的混沌工程测试，而非意外的系统故障。", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on my analysis of the metric data during the anomaly period, I've identified several significant issues. Here's my comprehensive assessment:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in client_error_ratio and error_ratio metrics indicating service errors\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 26.46 (200% change), error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 26.46 (200% change)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client_error_ratio and error_ratio metrics showing service degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 19.47 (200% change), error_ratio p99 increased from 0.0 to 19.47 (200% change)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Severe response time degradation with rrt and rrt_max metrics\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt median increased from 3225.93 to 13403.61 (122.4% change), rrt_max median increased from 42246.0 to 130879.0 (102.39% change)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"High CPU usage and response time issues with pod_cpu_usage and rrt metrics\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage median increased from 0.0 to 0.6 (200% change), rrt median increased from 5430.34 to 11184.3 (69.26% change)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"CPU usage and response time degradation with pod_cpu_usage and rrt_max metrics\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage median increased from 0.0 to 0.6 (200% change), rrt_max median increased from 41857.0 to 90423.0 (73.43% change)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory pressure indicated by node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes reduction\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes median decreased from 13109424128.0 to 7922741248.0 (49.32% reduction)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Response time spike with rrt_max metric showing performance degradation\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99 increased from 7239.52 to 47772.1 (147.36% change)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## Key Findings:\n\n1. **Multiple Service Errors**: `productcatalogservice-0` and `cartservice-0` show significant error ratio increases, suggesting service-level issues.\n\n2. **AdService Performance Crisis**: All three `adservice` pods (`adservice-0`, `adservice-1`, `adservice-2`) show severe response time degradation and CPU usage spikes.\n\n3. **Node Memory Pressure**: `aiops-k8s-08` node shows significant memory reduction, which may be contributing to the performance issues.\n\n4. **CurrencyService Latency**: `currencyservice-0` exhibits extreme response time spikes at the p99 percentile.\n\nThe most critical issues appear to be the AdService cluster-wide performance degradation and the error rates in ProductCatalog and Cart services, potentially exacerbated by memory pressure on node `aiops-k8s-08`."}
